%% Séquence — Inscription, connexion et validation d'email (EduTutor IA)
sequenceDiagram
  actor E as Étudiant
  participant F as Frontend React
  participant A as API DRF (accounts)
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant M as Email (Brevo / console)

  E->>F: Saisit email + mot de passe (inscription)
  F->>A: POST /api/accounts/signup/
  A->>DB: Crée User (username = email) + Profile (email_verified = false)
  A->>M: Envoie l'email de validation (lien signé)
  A-->>F: 201 Created (user)

  E->>F: Connexion (email + mot de passe)
  F->>A: POST /api/accounts/login/
  A->>DB: Vérifie les identifiants
  A-->>F: 200 { token, user }
  F->>F: Stocke le token (localStorage)

  E->>M: Clique le lien de validation
  M->>A: GET /verify-email?token=...
  A->>DB: Profile.email_verified = true
  A-->>E: Email confirmé
